  "texts": [
    "The E2E dataset serves as a training resource for natural language generation systems tailored to the restaurant domain.",
    "Inputting data pertaining to restaurants enables the generation of sentences that articulate diverse information about the restaurant.",
    "The textual content within the dataset is meticulously composed, showcasing an extensive vocabulary and syntactic variety.",
    "• WebNLG (Gardent et al, 2017).",
    "Much like DART, the WebNLG dataset serves the purpose of mapping data to text."
  ]
}